Class OscP5Wrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.chrisjr.loom.wrappers.OscP5Wrapper

  • public class OscP5Wrapper
extends Object
    Author:
    chrisjr Holds either an actual oscP5 instance or an OscP5Recorder. This allows us to avoid importing oscP5 in sketches where it is not used.
